YATENGA FRENCH BAR & BISTRO

WELCOME TO YATENGA FRENCH BISTRO & BAR - A CASUAL EATERY SERVING FRENCH COMFORT FOOD. A NEIGHBORHOOD CULINARY TREASURE THAT COMBINES TIMELESS CLASSICS WITH THE SOUL OF HARLEM. BROUGHT TO YOU BY THE OWNERS OF SHRINE, SILVANA & OUAGA SPORTS BAR.

WEEKEND BRUNCH

Pop in on the weekends for brunch on the patio (or inside). Serving up some Harlems best breakfast specials, plus select unlimited cocktails at just $36.40 per person!

DINNER

ABOUT YATENGA

French comfort food in a delightful shabby chic, world bohemian setting. With whitewashed brick walls and exposed Edison bulbs, Yatenga's decor sets the tone for a delicious meal, dished up by Chef Gregorio Sanchez. Beloved by locals, our dynamic staff and friendly patrons will quickly bring newcomers into its fold. Enjoy a patio brunch on the weekend or cozy up inside with a date and a signature cocktail. Celebrating? Our communal table is ideal for hosting large groups in an intimate environment.

SISTER SPOTS

CHECK OUT OUR SISTER SPOTS RIGHT HERE IN HARLEM!
FROM LIVE MUSIC, DJ SETS TO SPORTS BARS 

SILVANA

Silvana is a Middle Eastern cafe and boutique, atop a bar/lounge and live music venue. All in one day, you can enjoy organic coffees and teas, pick up unique gifts from around the world, eat delicious Middle Eastern food, listen to live music, and drink craft cocktails.

SISTER SPOTS

SHRINE WORLD MUSIC VENUE

Shrine World Music Venue is a restaurant/bar and live music venue in the heart of Harlem. On any given night, one might be treated to the live sounds of classic big band jazz, roots reggae, old school funk, a folk singer-songwriter or contemporary soul.

OUAGA SPORTS BAR

Ouaga Sports Bar is a reimagining of local bars in Ouagadougou, Burkina Faso. It’s a unique and intimate venue to watch the world’s biggest competitive sporting events, as well as for niche fans to view their favorite sports.
